New Zealand’s September Residential Property Statistics

-- B y   D a n i e l   P e t r i e
-- 
2011-10-11T23:12:53Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-11/new-zealand-s-september-residential-property-statistics-table-.html
Following is a summary of  New Zealand ’s
September residential property statistics by cities, according to figures
from Quotable Value New Zealand Ltd., the government valuation agency.  Note: The annual growth in residential property values are calculated based  on residential sales entered into Quotable Value’s system for the  3-month period compared to the same period of the previous year.  Average sale prices are calculated based on residential sales entered  into QV’s system for the previous 3-month period. Prices are in  New Zealand dollars.  Monthly percent changes for sale prices are calculated by Bloomberg.  Source: Quotable Value New Zealand Ltd.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Daniel Petrie in Sydney at   dpetrie5@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Marco Babic at   mbabic@bloomberg.net  